## Overview
CloudTech Audit Framework is a Python-based tool designed to **evaluate cloud-based SaaS platforms**. It performs:
- **Architecture analysis** (API structure, database optimization, CI/CD review)
- **Cloud cost estimation** (AWS, Azure, GCP cost modeling)
- **Security review** (IAM policies, data encryption, network security)

## Features
✔ Supports **AWS, Azure, and GCP**  
✔ Generates **PDF reports** with architecture and cost insights  
✔ Scans **security vulnerabilities** in cloud configurations  

## Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/CloudTech-Audit-Framework.git
cd CloudTech-Audit-Framework
pip install -r requirements.txt
